OL,6,FWhy the data disparity?
OL,8,FOfficial adult obesity statistics in
OL,9,FWales are entirely based on self-
OL,10,Freported data. This means it is up to
OL,11,Fthe individual to accurately report
OL,12,Ftheir health information.
OL,14,FAccording to the, studies from across
OL,15,Fthe globe have shown people to
OL,16,Funderestimate their weight and
OL,17,Foverestimate their height when asked
OL,18,Fto self-report.
