OL,6,FObesity rates are also increasing
OL,7,Famong children, with the chief medical
OL,8,Fofficer for Wales, Sir Frank Atherton,
OL,9,Freporting in 2023 that nearly one in
OL,10,Fthree children are overweight or obese
OL,11,Fby the time they start primary school.
OL,13,FAccording to Nesta, the data also
OL,14,Faligns with obesity rates among
OL,15,Fchildren, which are also considerably
OL,16,Fhigher than in both England and Wales
OL,17,Fand based on professional measurements.
