OL,6,FThe charity is calling for new First
OL,7,FMinister to prioritise tackling
OL,8,Fobesity by working with other nations
OL,9,Fon "UK-wide innovative approaches".
OL,11,FJonathan Bone, speaking on behalf of
OL,12,FNesta Cymru, said: "To make good
OL,13,Fdecisions on public health, you need
OL,14,Fgood data.
OL,16,F"Having consistent reporting of public
OL,17,Fhealth data is important and the Welsh
OL,18,FGovernment's current approach means
OL,19,Fthat they could be underestimating the
OL,20,Fimpact of obesity, including for
OL,21,Fpeople aged over 55.
